# SEO Improvement Plan (Bing Webmaster Tools feedback)

Bing Webmaster Tools has identified issues with titles being too short and missing meta descriptions. This plan aims to enhance the metadata for better SEO performance.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] Metadata & Layout

#### [MODIFY] [layout.tsx](file:///Users/atsushishindo/Desktop/GovSearch/gov_hachiouji/src/app/layout.tsx)
- [x] Update `metadata.title` to be more descriptive and longer (e.g., "東京都+全市区町村 行政情報 横断検索 | hazimeru.net").
- [x] Refine `metadata.description` for clarity and keyword density.
- [x] Remove manual `<head>` tag to prevent potential conflicts with Next.js metadata injection.
- [x] Move Google Analytics `Script` tags to follow Next.js best practices (placed in the layout body).
- [x] Add `viewport` metadata explicitly to ensure compatibility.

