## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run build` to generate the static files.
- Inspect the generated `out/index.html` and `out/policy.html` using `grep` to ensure:
    - `<title>` is present and contains the new descriptive text.
    - `<meta name="description" ...>` is present in the `<head>` section.
- Verify that Google Analytics scripts still load correctly by checking the rendered HTML.

### Manual Verification
- Ask the user to deploy the updated files and check Bing Webmaster Tools after crawl.
